long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Pocket Jump is a fun arcade game where we try to get points by jumping upwards by overcoming obstacles with a character.
There is a miniature character in the game. With this character, we try to climb up by overcoming the obstacles from the siege. As we climb up, we get points. We continue to play by maintaining our high score goal with the points we have achieved. Pocket Jump is a skill game created, considering it a fun but challenging arcade game.
